<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA59">
<l>aruḷpurinta cintai yaṭiyārmēl vaittu</l>
<l>poruṭerintu kāṇkuṟṟa vappō – tiruṭirintu</l>
<l>nōkkiṉē ṉōkki niṉaintēṉa toṇkamala</l>
<l>mōkkiṉē ṉeṉṉaiyumaṅ kōrntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Directing my mind which longs for grace on [his] servants,</l>
<l>understanding the meaning at that time [I] had the sight, roaming in the darkness</l>
<l>I looked; looking, I thought and considering, ‘that is the bright lotus’</l>
<l>I thus raised myself.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
